Syntax: drink <liquid> {container}
Syntax: quaff <liquid> {container}

The drink and quaff command are synonymous and are used to quench a thirst.  
You must have a drink container or other liquid container handy.  
Alternatively, you may drink from some large liquid-container in the region
such as a lake, pond, stream or fountain.

See Also: SIP, EAT, POTIONS
Related Topics: OBJECT MANIPULATION
